data.title: Recall 029 2023 Labels
data.meta_description: Recall 029 2023 Labels - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. This document provides product recall information for two Brookside meat products - Brookside Fully Cooked Natural Casing Beef Wieners and Brookside Hot Beef Smoked Sausage. It identifies the UPC bar codes and lot/batch numbers to check for recall at the store and warehouse level, and describes how individual packages can be identified by consumers. The recall is related to a missing milk allergen label on the Beef Wieners product.
